title: Number of households in the U.S. 2015 , by age of householder
summary: The Number households Age in the 2015 by was Age 30_to_34_years_old , who made 23.57 households .
The most households Age was 45_to_54_years_old , with just 6.37 households .

In second place was Age 25_to_29_years_old with 9.35 households ; third place went to Age 15_to_24_years_old with 6.37 households ; fourth place went to Age 75_years_old_and_over with 13.06 households and fifth place went to Age 35_to_44_years_old , who was 21.12 households .
gold: This graph shows the number of households in the U.S. by age of householder in 2015 . In 2015 , about 10.73 million households were led by a person between 30 and 34 years old .
